rows.label: qst101204_msg0002
rows.name:
The bad-tasting soil suddenly
became delicious, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0003
rows.name:
Mo?! The poisonous water was flowing
from the Superbian base, mo?!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0004
rows.name:
Momo... It was Superbia's
fault that I couldn't grow
vegetables all this time, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0005
rows.name:
They buy the vegetables I
worked so hard to grow for
cheap... my hard work...

rows.label: qst101204_msg0006
rows.name:
But there's no point complaining
to you about it, mo.

rows.label: qst101204_msg0007
rows.name:
Don't worry about it, mo! My
grandma used to say that's when
you have to try your hardest, mo.

rows.label: qst101204_msg0008
rows.name:
Mo! I planted new seeds
in the field, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0009
rows.name:
I need your help with the
fertilizer again, mo.

rows.label: qst101204_msg0050
rows.name:
Still not enough nutrients, mo~
I'm waiting for fertilizer, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0060
rows.name:
The nutrients are perfect
now, mo! Thank you, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0061
rows.name:
It should grow bigger overnight, mo!
Come back after a good sleep, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0101
rows.name:
Will you give me some fertilizer,
mo? Different things have
different nutrients, mo.

rows.label: qst101204_msg0102
rows.name:
Still not enough nutrients, mo~
I'm waiting for fertilizer, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0103
rows.name:
The nutrients are perfect
now, mo! Thank you, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0104
rows.name:
It should grow bigger overnight, mo!
Come back after a good sleep, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0201
rows.name:
Thanks for your help, mo! Lots of
fertilizer, lots of nutrients, mo!

rows.label: qst101204_msg0202
rows.name:
It should grow bigger overnight, mo!
Come back after a good sleep, mo!
